---
title: Sticky Korean Chicken & Corn Slaw with Fried Egg & Soy Mayo
description: This chicken is dressing to impress anyone who sits at your table. A rainbow slaw tossed with the sweet and smokey taste
of charred sweetcorn holds up the succulent Korean stir-fry sauced chicken, wearing nothing less than a creamy soy mayo drizzle.
Don’t forget the jewel in the ensemble, the fried egg.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663d5cdff511de711bbb37ce-6bc0e1b9.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/663d5cdff511de711bbb37ce-en-NZ.pdf
